Package: bnmr
Type: Package
Title: A package to conduct Bayesian Mendelian randomization based on Bayesian Network using GWAS data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sun Jianle
Maintainer: The package maintainer <sjl-2017@sjtu.edu.cn>
Description: A package to conduct causal estimation between exposure and outcome across GWAS data using BNMR model, including the variants filtering via Bayesian network in the learning stage, as well as the effect size estimation through a revised Bayesian Mendelian randomization framework with imperfect instruments in the inference stage.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: False
Imports:
    bnlearn,
    rstan,
    MendelianRandomization,
    plyr,
    dplyr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
